list.name: Default
list.comment: replaced boost threads with std threads, replaced boost random with std random, faster RandomUniformGenerator (4x faster)

task.summary: Bug fixes (no dead lock in waiting, better exit for screenouput, memory usage in testmanager corrected, renaming of StringHelper functions)
added real online mode for DDTs
added splitting to the TestManager, now a dataset can be a split of many sets
ORF update now compatible with TestManager, added ScreenOuput for ORF predict
added real online learning for ORFs
started PoolInfo for Online Storage (logic missing),change to better Singleton Model, removed push_back
Fixed bug in GlobalStopWatch (if used in multithread functions)
more pool for online storage (not done yet), basic algorithm works
Pooling for Online Storage Basic Version works, renamed some stuff to better fit convention, removed some old code
Speed up build process, by introducing a flag, to not build old code
PoolInfo now as Observer for OnlineRandomForest after each update, the pool is updated according to the performance on the validation set (80 % done)
online pool update now works, changes the amount of points used for each class, based on the performance (still one minor bug, with the use of the data in the trees)

pool now uses avg number instead of performance result of last test, fixed bug for performance measurement of pool, better Singleton template instead of macro, SharedPtr now in KernelBase, logger and screenouput now count instead of just repeat errors and special lines
replaced boost threads with std threads, replaced boost random with std random, faster RandomUniformGenerator (4x faster)
